[
    {
        "name": "environment_variables",
        "description": "允许智能体感知、修改和创建环境变量（包括任务变量和智能体变量），作为决策和状态管理的基础",
        "type": "core",
        "provider": "default",
        "parameters": {
            "operation": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "操作类型",
                "enum": [
                    "list",
                    "set",
                    "add"
                ]
            },
            "variable_scope": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "变量作用域",
                "enum": [
                    "task",
                    "agent"
                ]
            },
            "variable_name": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "变量名称"
            },
            "variable_value": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "变量值"
            }
        },
        "response_format": {
            "success": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "description": "操作是否成功"
            },
            "variables": {
                "type": "object",
                "description": "变量列表或操作结果"
            }
        },
        "examples": [
            {
                "input": {
                    "operation": "list",
                    "variable_scope": "task"
                },
                "output": {
                    "success": true,
                    "variables": {
                        "project_deadline": "2023-12-31",
                        "budget_remaining": "50000"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "input": {
                    "operation": "set",
                    "variable_scope": "task",
                    "variable_name": "project_deadline",
                    "variable_value": "2024-01-15"
                },
                "output": {
                    "success": true,
                    "variables": {
                        "previous_value": "2023-12-31"
                    }
                }
            }
        ],
        "settings": {
            "audit_trail": true,
            "refresh_rate": "per_round"
        }
    },
    {
        "name": "workspace_management",
        "description": "Agent project workspace management capability, including file storage and retrieval for personal workspaces and shared workspaces.\n\n## Access Control\n**You can only access files within the following directories:**\n- `{task_workspace}/` (your task workspace)\n\n**Any attempt to access paths outside these directories will fail with an \"Access denied\" error.**\n\n## Workspace Structure\n```\n{task_workspace}/\n{agent_workspace_structure}├── ProjectSummary.md              # Project conclusions and key decisions\n└── ProjectIndex.md                # Directory structure and file locations\n```\n\n## Key Files\n{agent_workspace_files}- `ProjectSummary.md`: Project conclusions and key decisions\n- `ProjectIndex.md`: Directory structure and file locations\n\n## Important: File Path Rules\n1. **Always use full paths** starting with `{task_workspace}/`\n2. **Correct path example**: `{task_workspace}/ProjectSummary.md`\n3. **Wrong path example**: `ProjectSummary.md` (relative paths will fail!)\n4. **Wrong path example**: `/backend/ProjectSummary.md` (outside allowed directories!)\n{agent_workspace_usage}\n\n## Current Project Structure\n```\n{project_index_content}\n```\n\n## Tool Usage Guide\n\n### edit_file Tool\n**Important:** When editing files, it is recommended to first use the `dryRun: true` parameter to preview changes before actually executing.\n\n**Key: edits Parameter Format Requirements**\n- `edits` must be a **real JSON array**, not a string!\n- Wrong example: `\"edits\": \"[{...}]\"` (this is a string, will cause an error!)\n- Correct example: `\"edits\": [{...}]` (this is an array)\n- Each array element must contain `oldText` and `newText` fields\n- `oldText` must **exactly match** the text in the file (including spaces and newlines)\n- It is recommended to first use `read_file` to read the file content to ensure `oldText` is accurate\n\n**Correct edit_file call format:**\n```json\n{\n  \"path\": \"{task_workspace}/filename.md\",\n  \"edits\": [\n    {\n      \"oldText\": \"exact matching old text\",\n      \"newText\": \"replacement new text\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"dryRun\": true\n}\n```\n\n**Wrong format (will cause Invalid arguments error):**\n```json\n{\n  \"path\": \"{task_workspace}/filename.md\",\n  \"edits\": \"[{\\\"oldText\\\": \\\"...\\\", \\\"newText\\\": \\\"...\\\"}]\"\n}\n```\n\n### Usage Tips\n- Use `read_file` to get the current file content first\n- Use `edit_file` with `dryRun: true` to preview changes before applying\n- Use `list_directory` tool to list files in a directory\n- Update key decisions and results to `ProjectSummary.md`\n- Create new files and organize the project directory as needed",
        "type": "core",
        "provider": "default",
        "parameters": {
            "workspace_type": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Workspace type",
                "enum": [
                    "personal",
                    "shared",
                    "both"
                ]
            },
            "content": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Project file content to store"
            }
        },
        "response_format": {
            "success": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "description": "Whether storage was successful"
            },
            "file_id": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Unique identifier of the project file"
            }
        },
        "examples": [
            {
                "input": {
                    "workspace_type": "personal",
                    "content": "The customer emphasized that product security is the top priority"
                },
                "output": {
                    "success": true,
                    "file_id": "workspace-12345"
                }
            }
        ],
        "settings": {
            "retention_policy": "importance_based",
            "dynamic_placeholders": [
                "task_workspace",
                "agent_workspace_structure",
                "agent_workspace_files",
                "agent_workspace_usage",
                "project_index_content"
            ]
        }
    },
